{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 178,
      "text": "And this was the work that I did while-- while I was in Majdanek, all the time there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 179,
      "text": "We were only there for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 180,
      "text": "It was long enough, believe me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 181,
      "text": "But six weeks because they were folding up the camps while the Russians were advancing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 182,
      "text": "It was already Spring, 1945, March.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 183,
      "text": "And they were-- the crematorium, we could see that there was no smoke coming anymore from there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 184,
      "text": "And they sent-- before they sent us away, they sent the 100 young women away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 185,
      "text": "And they came to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 186,
      "text": "And they were so happy because they reasoned that if they wanted to kill them, they would have killed them here and there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 187,
      "text": "They have the facilities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 188,
      "text": "So if they're sending them away, it means it's a good sign, they sending them to another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 189,
      "text": "But it wasn't a good sign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 190,
      "text": "They sent them to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 191,
      "text": "And there, all 100 went straight to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 192,
      "text": "We found that out a few days later when we arrived in Auschwitz, because there were people who worked there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 193,
      "text": "And they told us, oh, those beauties from Majdanek, they were all sent to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 194,
      "text": "So they were happy for no reason at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 195,
      "text": "They-- they didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 196,
      "text": "And this is this very, very sad story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 197,
      "text": "And we were sent-- from Majdanek, we were sent to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Majdanek, my mom, my dad, and my younger sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, they were sent to Auschwitz straight away, those 100 girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were sent to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When we came later to Auschwitz, we were told about what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were-- in the meantime, we were sent to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were still four of us, my mother, my little sister, my father, and I.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
